It is necessary to compile both LLVM and VMKIT without the -fno-rtti compiler
flag for integrating Scilab V6+ and VMKIT.

1 - Configure LLVM following the standard instructions, but add REQUIRES_RTTI=1
as make parameter like:
$ cd LLVM-src/
$ ./configure # See docs
$ make REQUIRES_RTTI=1

2 - Re-configure VMKIT, by running ./configure again with all its configuration
parameters:
$ cd VMKIT-src/
$ ./configure # See docs
$ make
